{"word":"ἀποπτύω","slug":"ἀποπτύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποπτύω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to spit out</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>ἀπ. ἄχνην</el> <i>to vomit forth</i> foam, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to spit</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to abominate, loathe, spurn</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: aor1 <el>ἀπέπτυσα,</el> = <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>omen absit</el>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}